	</p>
	<p>
		Bonus 2:<br />
		<%= text_field_tag :bonus_2_percent, nil, :size => 3 %>% to month
		<%= text_field_tag :bonus_2_month, nil, :size => 3 %>
	</p>
	<p>
		Bonus 3:<br />
		<%= text_field_tag :bonus_3_percent, nil, :size => 3 %>% to month
